      </div>\n       </div> \n      </span></button>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <pre class=\"code-block-module__vF3MAa__pre\"><code class=\"grid text-[var(--ds-gray-1000)] text-left whitespace-pre break-normal !text-[13px] leading-[20px] font-mono hyphens-none\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><span class=\"line\"><span>npm</span><span> </span><span>install</span><span> </span><span>next@14</span></span></code></pre>\n  </div>\n  <p>There is no configuration option to disable the vulnerable code path.</p>\n  <h2 id=\"discovery\" data-docs-heading=\"\"><a href=\"#discovery\">Discovery<span> \n     <svg viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" height=\"0.7em\" width=\"0.7em\">\n      <g stroke-width=\"1.2\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\">\n       <path fill=\"none\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" d=\"M8.995,7.005 L8.995,7.005c1.374,1.374,1.374,3.601,0,4.975l-1.99,1.99c-1.374,1.374-3.601,1.374-4.975,0l0,0c-1.374-1.374-1.374-3.601,0-4.975 l1.748-1.698\"></path> <path fill=\"none\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" d=\"M7.005,8.995 L7.005,8.995c-1.374-1.374-1.374-3.601,0-4.975l1.99-1.99c1.374-1.374,3.601-1.374,4.975,0l0,0c1.374,1.374,1.374,3.601,0,4.975 l-1.748,1.698\"></path>\n      </g>\n     </svg> \n    </span></a></h2>\n  <p>Thank you to <a href=\"https://github.com/lachlan2k\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Lachlan Davidson<span class=\"inline-flex not-prose\"> \n     <svg data-testid=\"geist-icon\" height=\"16\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" style=\"color:currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\">\n      <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M6.75011 4H6.00011V5.5H6.75011H9.43945L5.46978 9.46967L4.93945 10L6.00011 11.0607L6.53044 10.5303L10.499 6.56182V9.25V10H11.999V9.25V5C11.999 4.44772 11.5512 4 10.999 4H6.75011Z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path>\n     </svg> \n    </span></a> for discovering and responsibly disclosing this vulnerability. We are intentionally limiting technical detail in this advisory to protect developers who have not yet upgraded.</p>\n  <h2 id=\"references\" data-docs-heading=\"\"><a href=\"#references\">References<span> \n     <svg viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" height=\"0.7em\" width=\"0.7em\">\n      <g stroke-width=\"1.2\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\">\n       <path fill=\"none\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" d=\"M8.995,7.005 L8.995,7.005c1.374,1.374,1.374,3.601,0,4.975l-1.99,1.99c-1.374,1.374-3.601,1.374-4.975,0l0,0c-1.374-1.374-1.374-3.601,0-4.975 l1.748-1.698\"></path> <path fill=\"none\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" d=\"M7.005,8.995 L7.005,8.995c-1.374-1.374-1.374-3.601,0-4.975l1.99-1.99c1.374-1.374,3.601-1.374,4.975,0l0,0c1.374,1.374,1.374,3.601,0,4.975 l-1.748,1.698\"></path>\n      </g>\n     </svg> \n    </span></a></h2>\n  <ul>\n   <li><a href=\"https://github.com/vercel/next.js/security/advisories/GHSA-9qr9-h5gf-34mp\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Next.js security advisory (CVE-2025-66478)<span class=\"inline-flex not-prose\"> \n      <svg data-testid=\"geist-icon\" height=\"16\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" style=\"color:currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\">\n       <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M6.75011 4H6.00011V5.5H6.75011H9.43945L5.46978 9.46967L4.93945 10L6.00011 11.0607L6.53044 10.5303L10.499 6.56182V9.25V10H11.999V9.25V5C11.999 4.44772 11.5512 4 10.999 4H6.75011Z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path>\n      </svg> \n     </span></a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-2025-55182\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">React security advisory (CVE-2025-55182)<span class=\"inline-flex not-prose\"> \n      <svg data-testid=\"geist-icon\" height=\"16\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" style=\"color:currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\">\n       <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M6.75011 4H6.00011V5.5H6.75011H9.43945L5.46978 9.46967L4.93945 10L6.00011 11.0607L6.53044 10.5303L10.499 6.56182V9.25V10H11.999V9.25V5C11.999 4.44772 11.5512 4 10.999 4H6.75011Z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path>\n      </svg> \n     </span></a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"https://react.dev/blog/2025/12/03/critical-security-vulnerability-in-react-server-components\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">React blog: Critical Security Vulnerability in React Server Components<span class=\"inline-flex not-prose\"> \n      <svg data-testid=\"geist-icon\" height=\"16\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" style=\"color:currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\">\n       <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M6.75011 4H6.00011V5.5H6.75011H9.43945L5.46978 9.46967L4.93945 10L6.00011 11.0607L6.53044 10.5303L10.499 6.56182V9.25V10H11.999V9.25V5C11.999 4.44772 11.5512 4 10.999 4H6.75011Z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path>\n      </svg> \n     </span></a></li>\n  </ul>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "React 服务器组件 (RSC) 协议中发现了一个严重远程代码执行 (RCE) 漏洞 (CVSS 10.0)，影响使用 App 路由器的 Next.js 应用，建议立即升级。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "React 服务器组件 (RSC) 协议中发现了一个严重远程代码执行 (RCE) 漏洞 (CVSS 10.0)，影响使用 App 路由器的 Next.js 应用，建议立即升级。",
  "summary": "本安全通告详细说明了一个严重的远程代码执行漏洞 CVE-2025-66478，该漏洞源于 React 服务器组件 (RSC) 协议中 React 官方代码的问题 (CVE-2025-55182)。此漏洞的 CVSS 评分为 10.0，允许未受信的输入影响未打补丁环境中的服务器端执行，可能导致 RCE。此漏洞特别影响在 15.x、16.x 版本以及从 14.3.0-canary.77 开始的金丝雀版本（用于小范围测试的预发布版本）上使用 App 路由器的 Next.js 应用。Next.js 13.x、14.x 稳定版、Pages 路由器应用和 Edge 运行时不受影响。Vercel 已经发布了修复版本（例如，15.0.5、16.0.7）来解决此问题。强烈建议所有受影响的用户升级到各自发布线中的最新修复版本，或者将金丝雀版本降级到稳定的 14.x 版本。在不升级的情况下，没有配置选项可以规避此漏洞。该通告特意省略了技术细节，以保护未打补丁的系统，并感谢 Lachlan Davidson 的负责任披露。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "RSC 协议中存在一个严重的 RCE 漏洞 (CVSS 10.0)，影响 Next.js App 路由器。",
      "explanation": "易受攻击的 RSC 协议允许未受信的输入触发意外的服务器端执行路径。这可能在特定的 Next.js 配置中导致远程代码执行。"
    },
    {
      "point": "特定的 Next.js 版本（15.x、16.x 和某些 14.3.0+ 金丝雀版本）容易受到攻击。",
      "explanation": "此漏洞影响在 15.x、16.x 版本以及从 14.3.0-canary.77 开始的金丝雀版本上使用 App 路由器的 Next.js 应用，而其他版本和配置不受影响。"
    },
    {
      "point": "建议立即升级到已修复的版本，目前没有其他临时解决方案。",
      "explanation": "用户必须升级到指定的已修复 Next.js 版本或将金丝雀版本降级到稳定的 14.x，因为没有配置选项可以禁用易受攻击的代码路径。"
